OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEx-Post Office boss missed 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchance to stop scandal     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former Post Office executive has said
OL,6, he regrets a "missed opportunity" to   
OL,7, halt the Horizon scandal in 2004.      
OL,9,FDavid Miller, a former Post Office     
OL,10,Fchief operations officer, told the     
OL,11,Fpublic inquiry into the Horizon scandal
OL,12,Fhe regretted not reading a report      
OL,13,Fcompiled by an IT expert.              
OL,15,FThe report found the IT system was     
OL,16,F"clearly defective".                   
OL,18,FMr Miller said had he read the report, 
OL,19,Fhe could have "taken action to address 
OL,20,Fthe issues raised".                    
